text: It’s two bus stop away from Redhill MRT. Stop by to perform Isyak prayer. الحمدلله imam just starting with Al Fatihah. I was rushing from Redhill MRT. I will come again during day time to experience. I love that imam recite Al Quran after prayer. Beautiful voice too.
Such a Kampong mosque in Singapore are not too many. This mosque has been upgraded with air corn inside the main hall. It's good especially when the weather is hot
Used to pass by the mosque on bus ride to Queenstown Library or school (Queenstown Secondary) before the road was changed to one with a dead end. Glad it hasn't been moved elsewhere.
Asalamualaikum, when ever I go to Jamek mosque I have the feeling of pease of mind,and more than that, very clean and tidy.

Convenient mosque near Alexandara road. Good if you're travelling to IKEA or any nearby places. The mosque is a bit small, but is usually not crowded (I went for Asr, haven't tried praying Friday prayers here).

Cat with soft fur also hangs around. Good for de-stressing. Public rented bikes are sometimes available parked in front.
